              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-5">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-rose-600 font-black text-2xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-black text-gray-900 text-base">Mobile wedding portfolio = 87% of couples browse on phones</p>
