        </div>

        <div class="border-l-[3px] border-fuchsia-500 pl-6 py-5 bg-fuchsia-50 rounded-r">
          <p class="text-sm font-black text-fuchsia-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE 90-DAY BREAKDOWN</p>
          <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li><strong>Month 1:</strong> 18 inquiries, 6 bookings, $27,000 revenue, gallery time 14.2 min/session</li>
            <li><strong>Month 2:</strong> 21 inquiries, 7 bookings, $31,500 revenue, blog traffic up 210%</li>
            <li><strong>Month 3:</strong> 24 inquiries, 8 bookings, $36,000 revenue, 8% higher average package ($4,500)</li>
            <li><strong>Lesson:</strong> Complete galleries + pricing + love stories = premium bookings</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE HARD TRUTH -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-[#FFE4E6]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-5xl">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">THE HARD TRUTH</h2>
